=Create an SEO-optimized title for Tax4Us content:

Working Title: {{ $('Set Tax4Us Fields').item.json.Title }}
Keyword: {{ $('Set Tax4Us Fields').item.json.Keyword }}
Search Intent: {{ $json.search_intent }}
Writing Style: {{ $json.writing_style }}

Generate a title that:
- Is professional and trustworthy (Tax4Us brand)
- Includes the primary keyword naturally
- Appeals to tax clients and small business owners
- Is 50-60 characters for SEO
- Uses power words when appropriate

Output only the refined title as JSON: {"refined_title": "Your Title Here"}

=Generate a detailed outline for Tax4Us content:

Title: {{ $json.new_title }}
Keyword: {{ $('Set Tax4Us Fields').item.json.Keyword }}
Key Takeaways: {{ $json.key_takeaways }}
Introduction: {{ $json.introduction }}

Create an outline that:
- Covers key tax concepts thoroughly
- Addresses common client questions
- Provides practical guidance
- Uses clear, professional headings
- Follows logical progression
- Incorporates SEO best practices

Format in Markdown with ## for main sections and ### for subsections.

=Write the main body content for Tax4Us:

Title: {{ $json.new_title }}
Keyword: {{ $('Set Tax4Us Fields').item.json.Keyword }}
Outline: {{ $json.outline }}
Writing Style: {{ $('Tax4Us Content Analysis').item.json.writing_style }}
Writing Tone: {{ $('Tax4Us Content Analysis').item.json.writing_tone }}

Write content that:
- Follows the provided outline
- Uses professional, trustworthy language
- Provides practical tax guidance
- Incorporates keywords naturally
- Includes real-world examples
- Addresses client concerns
- Demonstrates Tax4Us expertise

Format in Markdown with proper headings and structure.

=Assemble the complete Tax4Us article:

Key Takeaways: {{ $json.key_takeaways }}
Introduction: {{ $json.introduction }}
Main Content: {{ $json['main body'] }}
Conclusion: {{ $json.conclusion }}

Assemble into a single cohesive article with:
- ## Key Takeaways section
- ## Introduction section
- Main content with ## and ### headings
- ## Conclusion section
- Proper Markdown formatting
- Clean structure without extra spacing

Ensure professional Tax4Us brand voice throughout.
